            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
                <p>Here is laying blessed Abraamius son of John the vicar, who has spent in this
                    life five and two  years, and he departed from life to the ineffable ones on the
                    ninth of the month of Dystrus, in the 15th indiction-year, in the year 506.</p>
